      "comment": "SUNSET PARIS (7) finished second (30.09) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 6th there. Has a win and four minor placings from five starts from this draw. Better than last start and worth following up. ACE DELUXE (1) missed the frame latest when eighth at Mandurah (17.84) but scored three back at this track (17.63). Some good form is emerging from his last run. Bold showing expected. SPOTLESS WAYNE (8) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 6th and beaten 15 lengths at Cannington (30.93). Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. THIS BAD BOY (2) has definite claims at his first try at this circuit.",
